claim.claim-text:
An information processing apparatus, comprising:
search means for performing a device search;
display means for displaying search results of the device search by said search means;
generation means for generating tag information to be written into a short range wireless communication tag, using identification information of a device selected by a user based on the search results; and
writing means for writing the tag information generated by said generation means into the short range wireless communication tag with a short range wireless communication.

A method of controlling an information processing apparatus, comprising:
a search step of controlling the information processing apparatus to perform a device search;
a display step of displaying search results of the device search;
a generation step of generating tag information to be written into a short range wireless communication tag, using identification information of a device selected by a user based on the search results; and
a writing step of controlling the information processing apparatus so as to write the tag information generated in the generation step into the short range wireless communication tag with a short range wireless communication .
